dct_title_s: Plan de Paris a vol d'oiseau : reproduction artistique en élévations de toutes les rues, maisons et richesses artistiques de Paris
dct_description_sm: Bird's-eye view. Artistic reproduction, includes all the railroads, street names, detailed illustrations of the Seine and maritime life in Paris, and individual buildings. Also includes major landmarks.
